title: Possible To Date A Ranker?
description:
Description :
        Possible to Date a Ranker?at manhwawebsiteThe top-ranked player of a popular online game, (Jjamppong Soft Tofu Ramen,) is a high school girl named Myung Seong-ah. She wants to keep her ranking a secret from everyone around her, but on her first day of high school, she runs into Kang Han-joonher in-game nemesis, (Strong Joon.) Worried that Kang Han-joon might figure out her identity, she even considers dropping out of school. But then she meets Ahn Tae-ui, who looks exactly like her game character, (Jjamppong Soft Tofu Ramen,) and falls for him at first sight.Maybe you like !
